{
  "texts": [
    "An example prompt input is shown in Figure 2.",
    "D. Multi-Agent StrategyGPT achieves superior performance in solving individual tasks following instructional logic in a dialogue.",
    "However, highly sophisticated problems in real-world traffic analysis are challenging to tackle by directly adopting GPT's general intelligence.",
    "Here we introduce the multi-agent strategy in transportation scenarios, an innovative collaborative workflow incorporating GPT as different agents to work as a team, which simulates the human's real teamwork logistics in a research lab or industrial company.",
    "The overall objective is to decompose the original complex tasks into sub-tasks of different scopes and then assign each to a GPT agent expertized in the designated domain to solve by a streamlined, collaborative workflow."
  ]
}